  "detailed_description": "<strong>Dash Fleet</strong> is a simple and fun dashing action game.<br>Make your character dash left or right by clicking left or right mouse button, and fly through various obstacles. Collect coins that can help your progress, and earn achievements for a great performance.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dashing action game<br></li><li>Test your skills and reflexes by avoiding deadly totems<br></li><li>Multiple playable characters (more to come)<br></li><li>Minimalist pixel art design<br></li><li>Relaxing music<br></li><li>Never ending fun</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Dash Fleet</strong> is a simple and fun dashing action game.<br>Make your character dash left or right by clicking left or right mouse button, and fly through various obstacles. Collect coins that can help your progress, and earn achievements for a great performance.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dashing action game<br></li><li>Test your skills and reflexes by avoiding deadly totems<br></li><li>Multiple playable characters (more to come)<br></li><li>Minimalist pixel art design<br></li><li>Relaxing music<br></li><li>Never ending fun</li></ul>",
